        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Cost and Token Budget"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Stateful systems inject history into every prompt. Without controls, prompt token cost grows with conversation length. The table below illustrates the compounding effect for a 20-turn conversation with 100 tokens per turn."
          }
        ]
      },
